a.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:46:39.000Z","msg":"又話深圳得、又話上海得，<br />\n又話香港人葡萄中國城市超越晒，<br />\n小學雞幾廿年"},{"pid":"3831fc07d6b75088d5c4e8be0ec89e677369cf3b","tid":1389581,"uid":159216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:47:08.000Z","msg":"仲有<br />\n解放軍既武力未必勁過警犬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd16a597c18954d0cf4b37bdbe6f5946835ed1df","tid":1389581,"uid":6528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:47:09.000Z","msg":"全民8月5日大罷工！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雙普選應要排最頭！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民黑衫、口罩同頭盔，返工返學行街，唔擺工既日子一齊做，將抗爭帶入生活，保護示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番香港獨立呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n所有既問題，所有既恩怨，係我地呢代到解決哂啦，好嗎？<br />\n我地唔可以好似上一代咁，計好哂數50年後都死左啦，唔好理啦。<br />\n我地唔可以再咁自私咁，過埋2047都死左啦。<br />\n我想我地既下一代唔需要再為呢啲事再受苦啦，我只係希望下一代可以係呼吸住自由既空氣出世係呢個地球上。<br />\n<br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭"},{"pid":"a5f05ec47bde1399fb422a1b4b22320bcb5db632","tid":1389581,"uid":68822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:48:15.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ErY1NGl2p_M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DErY1NGl2p_M&d=z0v15oAQEaIuorZt047Ij3wIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=2f61e1ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ErY1NGl2p_M</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwGX_Vgq-1G0&d=z0v15oAQEaIuorZt047Ij3wIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=7f4c5121\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0</a><br />\n</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港！時代革命！<br />\nLiberate Hong Kong! <br />\nThe Revolution Of Our Times! </span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>五大訴求</strong></span></span></ins><br />\n 1. 徹底撤回逃犯修訂條例<br />\n 2. 釋放所有因反送中被捕人士並承諾永不追究<br />\n 3. 撤回612暴動定性<br />\n 4. 追究警察濫權濫暴(包括721元朗官警黑勾結事件)，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n 5. 立即實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins>Hongkongers 5 Demands:</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n1. Full Withdrawal of the Extradition Bill<br />\n2. Retraction of the Characterisation of the Protestas a Riot<br />\n3. Release all Arrested Protesters<br />\n4. Accountability for Police and Yuen Long White Shirts Brutality<br />\n5. Implement Dual Universal Suffrage<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/Rcba2Hh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRcba2Hh.png&h=a61a5d44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/fm6yf2o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffm6yf2o.jpg&h=67e4b0d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時間無多，政府拖字訣，想我地自亂陣腳，行動規模必須升級</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08310b19826f39b50e4b9afd536e5196ac6500bb","tid":1389581,"uid":186521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46b110f2bc353c6d96f6b61c658ad5ca956d160d","tid":1389581,"uid":9028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:37:33.000Z","msg":"【#新聞點評】北京會動用解放軍嗎？香港不是89年的天安門，也不是西藏、新疆和南蒙古。解放軍一步出軍營，美國將立即取消《香港政策法》，香港國際金融中心地位隨即毀於一旦，<strong>北京將失去香港這個最重要的境外投資來源地（香港每年佔中國 FDI 總數六至七成）、上巿集資地（2018年中國企業在香港上市集資IPO金額高達35萬億美元）、銀行貸款來源地（2018 年香港各銀行對中國大陸銀行和非銀行客戶的淨債權總額高達 7,130 億元港幣）和債券融資平台（2018年中國企業在香港發行的美元債券總額高達723 億美元）</strong>&mdash;&mdash; 北京深知這些龐大的金融資本利益，至今仍無法透過上海這個中國（而不是國際）金融中心來提供。當北京早已受困於中美貿易戰、資金鏈日益脆弱之時，香港國際金融中心地位之一髮，足以牽動中共政權之全身穩定。換言之，解放軍出營之日，就是中港攬炒之時。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#香港人 #反送中 #一國兩制 #香港自治 #新冷戰 #香港政策法 #香港人權民主法<br />\n#Hongkonger #NoExtradition #OCTS #HongKongAutonomy #NewColdWar #HKHRDA #StandWithHongKong"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:48:25.000Z","msg":"但前提係班外資真係捨得撤資，但依商人黎講，未必會因為出解放軍死人而撤，佢哋都需要香港黎吸中國嘅金<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港人唔應該將希望擺喺解放軍度以為可以攬炒，我地要靠自己，喺佢無正當理由出軍嘅前提下爭取普選"},{"pid":"eaab0945a1011a2227565e58c8066f7eef100fe9","tid":1389581,"uid":213142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:50:09.000Z","msg":"水炮車呢個皇牌仲未出，就唔會有解放軍"},{"pid":"7b4abc05c79e303e58ed0a9e0c63587bc276cc6c","tid":1389581,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:51:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">IF WE BURN, YOU BURN WITH US</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"4751b3b0c85607c2391e910cc739e065acec73c7","tid":1389581,"uid":185045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:52:13.000Z","msg":"外國人只係信香港的一國兩制法治精神<br />\n永遠都唔會信中國式的法治<br />\n<br />\n所以就算中國幾咁全力支持上海, 上海永遠都唔會做到香港的效果"},{"pid":"aacbce7bb69ea2bec41ad82b26c3fe372aa84cb1","tid":1389581,"uid":9028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi